	</dd>
	<dd><a name="comment_2725" ></a>
	<p><em><strong>Garth</strong> replies:</em> It's amazing how quick we are to point fingers at other people in or out of society, and form opinions with very little knowledge or understanding. </p> <p>There are criminals who are not in prison who will vote May 5th, as there will be people in prison who deserve to vote for one reason or another, who cannot. This, to me, is sad.</p> <p>I hope I never get prevented from democracy in a democratic country.<br /></p>
